OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy low cloud around to
OL,6,Fstart the day, but this soon burning
OL,7,Fback towards the eastern coast, where
OL,8,Fit may stay cloudy for much of the
OL,9,Fday. Elsewhere, some good sunny spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping, although sunshine may turn
OL,11,Fhazy later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAreas of low cloud will move
OL,14,Fwestwards from the coast overnight
OL,15,Fwith perhaps some isolated light
OL,16,Fdrizzle, but most areas likely
OL,17,Fremaining dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
