OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother cloudy start, but
OL,6,Fsimilar to Monday cloud will burn back
OL,7,Ftowards the coast to leave plenty of
OL,8,Fsunny spells for the rest of the day.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHazy
OL,11,Fsunshine during the days, with showers
OL,12,Fpossible, perhaps thundery at times,
OL,13,Fwith the greatest risk on Wednesday.
OL,14,FWind easing by Thursday. Becoming very
OL,15,Fwarm or hot inland once more.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
